OL,3,CPolice officer injured after being
OL,4,C'intentionally' struck by vehicle
OL,6,FA police officer has received hospital
OL,7,Ftreatment for an injury caused by a
OL,8,Fmember of the public "intentionally"
OL,9,Fstriking them with their vehicle
OL,10,Fbefore driving off.
OL,12,FThe male officer was driving along
OL,13,FConscience Lane towards Devizes in a
OL,14,Fmarked police car when he spotted a
OL,15,Fvehicle in a field at about 11:30pm on
OL,16,FSaturday 1 June.
