OL,3,CPolice officer injured after being
OL,4,C'intentionally' struck by vehicle
OL,6,F"We are providing ongoing welfare
OL,7,Fsupport to the officer and their
OL,8,Ffamily. Our thoughts are with him and
OL,9,Fwe wish him a speedy recovery.
OL,11,F"We are currently undertaking
OL,12,Fextensive urgent inquiries to identify
OL,13,Fthe person responsible for this
OL,14,Fincident and we would encourage anyone
OL,15,Fwith information to come forward."
